    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Rendering List of Elements in React With JSX]]></title>
    <link href="http://jasonjl.me/blog/2015/04/18/rendering-list-of-elements-in-react-with-jsx/"/>
    <updated>2015-04-18T19:43:14-07:00</updated>
